commands.name: az security security-connector devops gitlabgroup list
commands.summary: List GitLab groups onboarded to the connector.
commands.syntax:
az security security-connector devops gitlabgroup list --name
                                                       --resource-group
                                                       [--max-items]
                                                       [--next-token]

commands.name: az security security-connector devops gitlabgroup list-subgroups
commands.summary: Gets nested subgroups of given GitLab Group which are onboarded to the connector.
commands.syntax:
az security security-connector devops gitlabgroup list-subgroups [--group-name]
                                                                 [--ids]
                                                                 [--name]
                                                                 [--resource-group]
                                                                 [--subscription]

commands.name: az security security-connector devops gitlabgroup show
commands.summary: Get a monitored GitLab Group resource for a given fully-qualified name.
commands.syntax:
az security security-connector devops gitlabgroup show [--group-name]
                                                       [--ids]
                                                       [--name]
                                                       [--resource-group]
                                                       [--subscription]
